text: The following is a list of notable events and releases of the year 1914 in Norwegian music. ==Events== ==Deaths== ==Births== ; February * 17 – Magne Elvestrand, pianist and harpsichordist, best known as an organist (died 1991). ; Juni * 24 – Kari Diesen, actor and singer (died 1987). ; November * 14 – Leif Solberg, classical composer and organist (died 2016). ==See also== * 1914 in Norway * Music of Norway ==References== Category:Norwegian music Norwegian Music Category:1910s in Norwegian music
